T

TDSampler - Class in com.ebizance.tdsampler
Command line application to run Thread dump sampler.

Usage: java -Dlog4j.configuration=file:../conf/log4j.properties -jar ../lib/TDSampler-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar [file|dir]

-Arguments-
file: Specify stack file path (e.g: C:/temp/test05-30-3/td.30052012_14_00_57.txt).

Thread - Class in com.ebizance.tdsampler.model
This is a POJO representing the current parsed thread.
This object is loaded into drools engine so it can be used to filter threads to parse (e.g.: filter by name).
